name: Climb the Metamorphosis of Narcissus
description:
Game that lets the player climb and explore Syzguru11's rendering of Metamorphosis of Narcissus by Salvador Dali 

W, A, S, D to move, Space to jump, shift runs, Mouse to steer.   Plays in your web browser.

Not if this will work on mobile devices.

Metamorphosis of Narcissus / Dali by Syzguru11
